msgstr "Realizado"

#: templates/challenges/challenge_how_it_works.html:126
msgid "Points locked in when a market resolves or you exit a forecast early."
msgstr ""
"Puntos fijados cuando un mercado se resuelve o sales temprano de un "
"pronóstico."

#: templates/challenges/challenge_how_it_works.html:129
#: templates/challenges/partials/challenge_leaderboard.html:24
#: templates/challenges/partials/challenge_leaderboard.html:55
#: templates/challenges/partials/challenge_leaderboard.html:155
#: templates/challenges/partials/standings_table.html:11
msgid "Unrealized"
msgstr "No realizado"

#: templates/challenges/challenge_how_it_works.html:130
msgid "Live estimate on open markets — updates as odds move."
msgstr ""
"Estimación en vivo en mercados abiertos — se actualiza cuando cambian las "
"cuotas."

#: templates/challenges/challenge_how_it_works.html:135
msgid ""
"Your challenge total is <strong class=\"text-slate-800 dark:text-"
"slate-200\">realized + unrealized</strong> across all events in the duel. "
"The leaderboard inside each challenge shows both columns."
msgstr ""
"Tu total del desafío es <strong class=\"text-slate-800 dark:text-"
"slate-200\">realizado + no realizado</strong> en todos los eventos del "
"duelo. La clasificación dentro de cada desafío muestra ambas columnas."

